- cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is also a likely category as the paper mentions attaining competitive translation quality for several language pairs, which could involve information retrieval techniques.
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is a possible category as the paper uses a model for bilingual lexicon extraction.
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper deals with natural language processing and machine translation.
- cs.DL (Machine Learning) is also a possible category as the paper may involve deep learning techniques for bilingual lexicon extraction.
